title: Episode 18 The Lost Episodes w August Alsina and Mila J
itunes:title: Episode 18 The Lost Episodes w August Alsina and Mila J
description:
The Lip Service crew is out on vacation this week, so we are having a flashback to when Lip Service podcast first started! You’ve heard parts of the August Alsina episode before and now we have the entire episode for your listening pleasure. We also have a never heard before Mila J episode that you don’t want to miss. The Lip Service crew will be back next week with another fresh episode. Enjoy!
